title: Quick Take: What Happened in Nevada and South Carolina
description: A wrap and look forward following Saturday's GOP Primary in South Carolina and Democratic caucus in Nevada. This episode: national political editor Mara Liasson, digital political reporter Danielle Kurtzleben, and campaign reporter Asma Khalid with campaign reporter and host Sam Sanders. Find the team on Twitter @MaraLiasson, @titonka, @asmamk, @samsanders, and at npr.org/politics - or email the show at nprpolitics@npr.org.
